    "### Arithmetische Ausdrücke\n",
    "\n",
    "Beispiel:\n",
    "```java\n",
    "5 * 3 / -7 % (2 + 1);\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "Binäre Operatoren:\n",
    "\n",
    "``+`` Addition <br/>\n",
    "``-`` Subtraktion <br/>\n",
    "``*`` Multiplikation <br/>\n",
    "``/`` Division <br/>\n",
    "``%`` Modulo (Divisionsrest)\n",
    "\n",
    "Unäre Operatoren:\n",
    "\n",
    "`` + `` Identität ($+x = x$) <br/>\n",
    "`` - `` Vorzeichenumkehrung"
   ]
