    "### Zuweisungsoperatoren\n",
    "\n",
    "Arithmetische Operationen lassen sich mit Zuweisungen kombinieren\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "| &nbsp;   | Kurzform | Langform |\n",
    "|----|----------| ---------|\n",
    "|``+=`` | x += y | x = x + y |\n",
    "|``-=`` | x -= y | x = x - y |\n",
    "|``*=`` | x *= y | x = x * y |\n",
    "|``/=`` | x /= y | x = x / y |\n",
    "|``++`` | x++    | x = x + 1 |\n",
    "|``--`` | x-- | x = x -1 |\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "Spart Schreibarbeit, sollte aber nur spärlich verwendet werden. \n"
   ]
  },
